下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1299407a1b13d011d7e868cba754b643c14151","tid":677912,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"一花一世界"},{"pid":"935b8fa74a663770c8fa17e675825197e4a846e4","tid":677912,"uid":88263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"616897a778f146719c1a92508e810ddd6d1aae43","tid":677912,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a95778f78acfce31991b68c8d8ff795698e799b4","tid":677912,"uid":88263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0eae2b342c446bef55d9ce270773972be2dd9973","tid":677912,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:12:57.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，想問下佛教入面係咪assume咗生物數量，包括細菌既數量係constant不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪關輪迴事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:15:48.000Z","msg":"生物數量只不過係個數字，施主何苦咁執著<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 探討下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"佛觀一砵水，八萬四千蟲<br />\n佛觀嗰砵水個砵又有幾大砵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大砵啲會唔會多啲蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乖啦，去行善積下善因啦，輪迴都係用嚟兇啲人做好事嘅啫，間唔中又有啲成咗佛上咗岸嘅佛得閒冇嘢做，想入返輪迴玩下，順手渡下啲人成佛，六道輪迴之中有幾多生物條數係計唔到㗎"},{"pid":"c1f1a544d9b2c5a4072925d980fe302a0901a18c","tid":677912,"uid":50060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"人點解要離苦?<br />\n<br />\n如果離苦 又點樣成為 尼釆所講既「超人」<br />\n<br />\n到底一個人應該要成為咩都懂得放下既「覺醒者」<br />\n<br />\n定係一個令自己受苦，每秒都超越自己既「超人」？"},{"pid":"684c65e1d1a364c8671c2d9052e32b41545f16c0","tid":677912,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"佛教都係宗教，都係冇撚腦的<br />\n唔正確，亦冇諗到咁細"},{"pid":"3cae0f9dad490a33196024874756def6b73375e6","tid":677912,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"616897a778f146719c1a92508e810ddd6d1aae43","tid":677912,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a95778f78acfce31991b68c8d8ff795698e799b4","tid":677912,"uid":88263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0eae2b342c446bef55d9ce270773972be2dd9973","tid":677912,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:12:57.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，想問下佛教入面係咪assume咗生物數量，包括細菌既數量係constant不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪關輪迴事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:15:48.000Z","msg":"生物數量只不過係個數字，施主何苦咁執著<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 探討下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"金剛經入面既：諸微塵，如來說非微塵，是名 微塵。 <br />\n微塵可以代生物數量入去理他，最後都係個名黎姐"},{"pid":"e1b93b1bc200e6db96a63c450e1faa21106dc760","tid":677912,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1f1a544d9b2c5a4072925d980fe302a0901a18c","tid":677912,"uid":50060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"人點解要離苦?<br />\n<br />\n如果離苦 又點樣成為 尼釆所講既「超人」<br />\n<br />\n到底一個人應該要成為咩都懂得放下既「覺醒者」<br />\n<br />\n定係一個令自己受苦，每秒都超越自己既「超人」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T03:49:01.000Z","msg":"唔放底，每一秒都喺慾望下驅使下行動<br />\n又何來超越自己?"},{"pid":"811bd46c1debe730876e847cfd917e4fc64a2ea2","tid":677912,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1f1a544d9b2c5a4072925d980fe302a0901a18c","tid":677912,"uid":50060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"人點解要離苦?<br />\n<br />\n如果離苦 又點樣成為 尼釆所講既「超人」<br />\n<br />\n到底一個人應該要成為咩都懂得放下既「覺醒者」<br />\n<br />\n定係一個令自己受苦，每秒都超越自己既「超人」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"所謂既離苦<br />\n<br />\n唔係真係離開左苦<br />\n<br />\n係你明白到點解苦<br />\n<br />\n但你依然都係苦當中<br />\n<br />\n只係你唔再怕苦<br />\n<br />\n咁離苦依一刻，你咪成為左尼采口中既「超人」<br />\n<br />\n因為你唔再恐懼苦 咁即使苦係你身邊 亦同唔係身邊冇分別了"},{"pid":"dd8227158b8cc1d9f6a983917bd721046418d6f4","tid":677912,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eae2b342c446bef55d9ce270773972be2dd9973","tid":677912,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:12:57.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，想問下佛教入面係咪assume咗生物數量，包括細菌既數量係constant不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪關輪迴事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"唔知乜屄經入面講過：<br />\n一個靈魂可以投胎入一隻豬、牛、羊、雞嗰啲大型動物度。<br />\n<br />\n但亦都可以化生做十萬八千隻鮑魚、海參、蜆。<br />\n<br />\n亦可以化生做一億八千萬隻奧米加變形蟲、大腸幹菌、幽門螺旋菌<br />\n<br />\n利申：耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}